#Basic info
Free (libre) resources related to the bachelor degree in "Computer Science" at UNIFE (University of Ferrara).

##University degree course
<unife.it/scienze/informatica/>

##List of courses
<unife.it/scienze/informatica/insegnamenti>

##Resources

Note: We are not responsible for the external resources. Some of that software, infact, does not state any license. For this reason that software is considered proprietary, even if that was not intended by the authors.

| Course | Free UNIFE | External links |
| --- | --- | --- |
| [Numerical Calculus and Laboratory](http://www.unife.it/scienze/informatica/insegnamenti/calcolo-numerico-i)| [numerical-calculus-octave-scripts](https://github.com/free-unife/numerical-calculus-octave-scripts) | |
| [Economics and Business Administration](http://www.unife.it/scienze/informatica/insegnamenti/economia-gestione-imprese) | [economics-and-business-administration](https://github.com/free-unife/economics-and-business-administration) | |
| [Operating Systems and Laboratory](http://www.unife.it/scienze/informatica/insegnamenti/sistemi-operativi-laboratorio) | | [rpadovani/chatFe](https://github.com/rpadovani/chatFe), [MochTor/ChatFE](https://github.com/MochTor/ChatFE), [davideorsini/chatFe-BattilanaOrsini](https://github.com/davideorsini/chatFe-BattilanaOrsini), [puskin94/chatFe-Bucci](https://github.com/puskin94/chatFe-Bucci) | 
| [Computer Graphics](http://www.unife.it/scienze/informatica/insegnamenti/grafica-computerizzata) | [threejs-waterfall](https://github.com/free-unife/threejs-waterfall), [threejs-sierpinski-tetrix](https://github.com/free-unife/threejs-sierpinski-tetrix) | [dannylessio/threejs-r78-template](https://github.com/dannylessio/threejs-r78-template), [MochTor/CG_Final_Project---EuroZero](https://github.com/MochTor/CG_Final_Project---EuroZero) |
| [Networks Laboratory](http://www.unife.it/scienze/informatica/insegnamenti/laboratorio-reti) | [networks-lab](https://github.com/free-unife/networks-lab) | |
| [Algorithms and data structures](http://www.unife.it/scienze/informatica/insegnamenti/algoritmi-strutture-dati) | [algorithms-and-data-structures](https://github.com/free-unife/algorithms-and-data-structures), [libncc](https://github.com/free-unife/libncc) | |
| [Databases I and Laboratory](http://www.unife.it/scienze/informatica/insegnamenti/basi-dati-1-laboratorio) | | [lovalova1991/AskUnife](https://github.com/lovalova1991/AskUnife) | |
